sentence: Steve Young, David Allan Coe, John Prine, Billy Joe Shaver, Gary Stewart, Townes Van Zandt, Kris Kristofferson, Michael Martin Murphey, Tompall Glaser, Steve Earle, and the later career renaissance of Johnny Cash, along with a few female vocalists such as Jessi Colter, Sammi Smith, Tanya Tucker, and Rosanne Cash.
